I would like to thank @mercedesamgf1 for the 5 years together. We have achieved quite some things, that I will never forget. I have learned a lot and you have made me stronger. I’m wishing you all the best for the future. And hey, we have still this season to Win! Let’s get it 💪

#VB77 #F1 #NeverGiveUp

node.text:
I’m very happy and excited to let you know that I’ll be joining @alfaromeoracingorlen @f1 team from 2022 with a multi year contract!

It’s new and exciting project for me. To get to the top together - I really can’t wait. I will give all my expertise and speed I can for the bright future of this iconic team and brand with impressive history in motorsports.

Press release link in bio.

#VB77 #F1 @alfaromeoracingorlen @alfaromeoofficial #NewChapter #NeverGiveUp
